## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9be00-132">這個屬性被以百分比表示 y 軸縮放比例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9be00-132">This property is measured as a percentage of the Y-axis scale.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9be00-133">根據預設，其值設為 25。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9be00-133">By default, its value is set to 25.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9be00-134">這表示會在使用刻度分欄摺疊數列中的資料點，只有在至少 25%的標尺的差異。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9be00-134">This means that data points in a series that have a difference of at least 25% of the scale will be collapsed with a scale break.</span></span>  
  
   
  
