## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9be00-155">下列程式碼範例示範如何設定與刻度斷層相關的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9be00-155">The following code example demonstrates how to set properties relating to the scale break.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9be00-156">假設<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>控制項新增至設計介面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9be00-156">It is assumed that the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control has been added to the design surface.</span></span>  
  
